American Grammy nominated rapper GoldLink will be performing at Rocking the Daisies 2018. The news was announced on Monday via the popular event's Twitter account with a large photo of DeAnthony Carlos otherwise known as GoldLink. THE TWEET READ: "Grammy nominated, platinum-selling rap artist GoldLink is headed to #RTD2018!" Tickets for the grand scale outdoor event recently went on sale and Channel24 Music sat down with organiser George Avakian who told us about changes to everything from camping to over how many days the festival takes place. Goldlink has played at Coachella and collaborated with Jazmine Sullivan and KAYTRANADA. Source: Channel24 Music